<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3858267>
    dc:description "Fig. 51. Bracon (Glabrobracon) titubans Wesmael (A-H: ♀ lectotype, I-K: ♀, L: ♀ / ♁). A. Head in dorsal view. B. Head in frontal view. C. Propodeum. D. Hind femur. E. Claw. F. Distal part of right forewing. G. First discal cell of right forewing. H. Tergites 1-3. I. Hind half of head in dorsal view. J. Hind femur. K. Second submarginal cell of right forewing. L. Tergites 2-3." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3858267/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3858193>
    dc:description "Fig. 16. Bracon (Lucobracon) larvicida Wesmael, 1838 (A-I: ♀ lectotype, J: ♀, K: ♀ / ♁). A. Head in dorsal view. B. Head in frontal view. C. Propodeum. D. Hind femur. E. Claw. F. Distal part of right forewing. G. First discal cell of right forewing. H. Tergites 1-3. I. Hind end of ovipositor apparatus. J. propodeum. K. First tergite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3858193/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3858217>
    dc:description "Fig. 28. Bracon (Glabrobracon) nigriventris Wesmael, 1838 (A-H: ♀ holotype, I: ♀, J: ♁). A. Head in dorsal view. B. Head in frontal view. C. Propodeum. D. Hind femur. E. Claw. F. Distal part of right forewing. G. First discal cell of right forewing. H. Tergites 1-3. I. Hind femur. J. First tergite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3858217/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3858221>
    dc:description "Fig. 29. — A-F. Bracon (Glabrobracon) nigriventris Wesmael, 1838 (A-B, D-E: ♀, C, F: ♁). A. Head in dorsal view. B-C. Distal part of right forewing. D-E. First discal cell of right forewing. F. Tergites 2-3. — G-I. Bracon (Glabrobracon) conjugellae Bengtsson, 1924, ♀ paralectotype. G. Head in dorsal view. H. Tergites 1-3. I. Hind femur." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3858221/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

